      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">4.2105</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li id="id1989H0Z10BA" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d326e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.204-24.dita#FAR_52_204_24"
                        base="id1989I600I4C"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>, Representation Regarding Certain Telecommunications and Video Surveillance Services or Equipmentâ€“</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d326e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                In all solicitations for contracts; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d326e24">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                Under indefinite delivery contracts, in all notices of intent to place an order, or solicitations for an order (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, subpart <xref href="Subpart_8.4.dita#FAR_Subpart_8_4"
                              base="i1117301"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.4</xref> and <xref href="16.505.dita#FAR_16_505"
                              base="i1104008"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d326e38">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.204-25.dita#FAR_52_204_25"
                        base="id1989I600I4C"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-25</xref>, Prohibition on Contracting for Certain Telecommunications and Video Surveillance Services or Equipment, in all solicitations and contracts.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d326e46">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.204-26.dita#FAR_52_204_26"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-26</xref>, Covered Telecommunications Equipment or Services-Representation, in all solicitations.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
